item.title: Am I Obama?
item.description: Browser Wars Browser-Users I’m not sure, but this guy looks like Obama. At least I’m a proud Opera-User. The new release has a feature I’ve needed multiple times before: You can now reopen a complete Window with all its tabs that you have accidently closed.
